      InternalsVisibleTo declaration on DcsvIo.D2.Geo.SourceGen.
      Build-only — analyzer/build assets do NOT propagate to consumers of
      this csproj (consistent with the other source-gen project references).
    -->
    <ProjectReference Include="..\geo\source-gen\DcsvIo.D2.Geo.SourceGen.csproj" />
